 <name>PEAR_Frontend_Gtk2</name>
 <channel>pear.php.net</channel>
 <summary>Graphical PEAR installer based on PHP-Gtk2</summary>
 <description>This program is a graphical frontend for PEAR, the PHP Extension
  and Application Repository. It uses PHP-Gtk2 as graphical toolkit
  and lets you easily browse available packages and install them
  on your computer.
  The program is designed to be by end-users, making it as easy as
  possible to install and uninstall programs.</description>
